    Median (Middle)       Middle of Series
    Mode (Most)           Most Used Number in Series
    Mean (Average)        Series Sum / Number = Mean
    Range (Difference)    Large Number - Small Number = Range

    M    Median  (Middle)          11 7 11 18 9 7 6 23 7 6 7 7 7"9"11 11 18 23   Median: 9
    Mo   Mode    (Most)            11 7 11 18 9 7 6 23 7 6"7 7 7"9 11 11 18 23   Mode: 7
    xÌ…    Mean    (Average)         11 + 7 + 11 + 18 + 9 + 7 + 6 + 23             Mean: 99/9 = 11
    R    Range   (Difference)      11 7 11 18 9 7 6 23 7 6 7 7 7 9 11 11 18 23   Range: 23-6 = 17    (Large:23, Small: 6)
         Outlier (Out There)       1  1 3  11 3 1                                Outlier: 11         Far from other values

